      <div id ="main-2">
  <p>Shadow Boxer (PC, June 2014)</p>
  <p>Language: Game Maker Language</p>
  <p>Team Size: 2</p>
  <p>Roles: Lead game designer, programmer and artist</p>
  <p>A 2D platformer with a twist where you cannot be in direct sunlight. I programmed the player, enemies, and a way the game can tell if the player is underneath the sun. Also, the game takes in consideration if the player built a structure over themselves to protect from the sunlight. I also created the art direction, sprites and level design.</p>
  <a href="http://people.ucsc.edu/~brlgomez/CMPS80K/final.exe">Download</a>
